				<td colspan="2"><span>Well, all I can say is that while I enjoy the downtime of not twisting 32 mana, replenishment and 30 Amp between battles, it has created near unbearable downtime for groups I'm in.  I say after buffing or rezing a wipe, a group now takes an additional 5 minutes to get back into the action.  
<br />

<br />
Now I've never (maybe once) had even 2 bards in the same group, let alone more than that, so I cannot speak to the multi-bard pumping mana situation, but if that was the problem, make it so that the 32 mana pulse doesn't stack with itself.  Not allowing it to stack with the icon Replenishment/Mar's is nothing short of game altering IMHO.  
<br />

<br />
I've sent feedback to this point, but I don't expect any changes.  Ah well, just another in the long list of nerfs.  
